{% block form %}

 <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Uploading your SR1 form</h1>
  
  <p class="govuk-body">Make sure the files you need are saved to the device 
  you are using to apply for Attendance Allowance.</p>
  <p class="govuk-body">The SR1 form has two pages. Make sure you upload them both.</p.>

  <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Taking photos or scans of your SR1 form</h1>

  <p class="govuk-body">If you are taking a photo or scan of your SR1 form, make sure:</p>

  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>all of the text can be read easily</li>
    <li>the photo or scan is not blurry</li>
    <li>each full page is visible, including all four corners</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="govuk-body">You will be able to upload more than one file if you need to.</p>

